<HL> PPG Buys Clorox Subsidiaries </HL>
<DD> 10/03/89 </DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J) </SO>
<CO> PPG CLX </CO>
<IN> TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
HOUSEHOLD AND PERSONAL-CARE PRODUCTS (HHP) </IN>
<DATELINE> PITTSBURGH  </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   PPG Industries Inc. said it completed the purchase of Clorox Co.'s Olympic HomeCare Products and Lucite HomeCare Products subsidiaries for $130 million. 

   The glass, coating and specialty-chemicals concern said the acquisition will double its consumer-paint business. 

</TEXT>
